New Items in Shadow Object --
 
setin, setout                   - sets login/out strings
sh, she                         - shadow talk/emote
sc, scs                         - local stats
ow                              - other who
shw                             - shadow who
shay                            - shadow speak
save_me, restore_me, update_me  - save, restore and update your mark
points                          - whether to use hps or not
mon                             - display monitor
info                            - info
dd                              - drain damage
time                            - displays the time
muffsh                          - muffle your fellow shadez
startme                         - start in guild hall or church
leave_shadows                   - don't try it ...

